Products.RichDescription:
Woolworths White Wraps are soft and made with Australian wheat flour.

4 Different ways to enjoy White Wraps.

1. Grilled Wrap. Keep warm with a toasty grilled wrap.

2. Quesadilla. Fold your wrap for Mexican fiesta with your family.

3. Pizza Base. Keep your wrap flat and make your own pizzas.

4. Fresh Wrap. Add your favourite fresh ingredients, perfect for breakfast on the go.

Source of fibre.

Product can be re-sealed.

Suitable for vegetarians.
